{
  "schema_version": "market_rules.v1",
  "updated_at": "2026-07-19",
  "source_notes": [
    "A-share fee defaults are configurable and should be confirmed with broker before live use.",
    "Hong Kong securities fees follow HKEX published fee categories; brokerage remains broker-configurable.",
